Field Detail

objects

public java.util.Map<DrawingPanel,java.util.List<VisualizationPrimitive>> objects
The JVObjects associated with this record, mapped by the JVDrawingPanels in which they occur. This exists for efficient linking of selections. When records are selected, the selected records (from DataTable.selectedRecords) are iterated through to be drawn. The JVDrawingPanel which is doing the drawing queries this map to see what it should draw to represent this record. Initially, this map is null.
